  <Section Title="Declaration">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[struct WindowInfoWayland : public IFrameBuffer::WindowInfoBase;]]></Code>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>WindowInfoWayland</TypeRef> structure describes a Wayland surface for framebuffer presentation.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      Availability: Linux or compatible Wayland platforms when <TypeRef>COBALT_RENDERER_WAYLAND_SUPPORT</TypeRef> is enabled. This is automatically enabled on Linux unless platform binding selection is manual.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
